      <title>Mac系统升级High Sierra导致Cocoapods不可用</title>
      <link href="/2018/04/15/Cocoapods-bug/"/>
      <url>/2018/04/15/Cocoapods-bug/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Mac系统升级到High-Sierra（10-13-4）之后Cocoapods报错"><a href="#Mac系统升级到High-Sierra（10-13-4）之后Cocoapods报错" class="headerlink" title="Mac系统升级到High Sierra（10.13.4）之后Cocoapods报错"></a>Mac系统升级到High Sierra（10.13.4）之后Cocoapods报错</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ pod setup</span><br><span class="line">zsh: /usr/local/bin/pod: bad interpreter: /System/Library/Frameworks/Ruby.framework/Versions/2.0/usr/bin: no such file or directory</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">``` </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">原因：</span><br><span class="line">旧的系统自带的是Ruby2.0，High Sierra的Ruby是2.3的，因此执行pod命令时会找不到Ruby解释器。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">解决：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$ sudo gem install cocoapods</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">然后</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$ pod setup</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">更新本地Cocoapods库</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">此时执行pod install 命令时，又报错：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Re-creating CocoaPods due to major version update.<br>Analyzing dependencies<br>[!] The dependency <code>SVProgressHUD</code> is not used in any concrete target.<br>The dependency <code>MJRefresh</code> is not used in any concrete target.<br>The dependency <code>SDWebImage</code> is not used in any concrete target.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">原因：</span><br><span class="line">Cocoapods升级到最新版本之后，podfile格式需要变化。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">解决：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>platform:ios, ‘8.0’<br>pod ‘SVProgressHUD’, ‘~&gt; 2.0.3’<br>pod ‘MJRefresh’, ‘~&gt; 3.1.0’<br>pod ‘SDWebImage’, ‘~&gt; 3.7.6’</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">改为：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>platform:ios, ‘8.0’</p><p>target ‘当前工程名’ do</p><p>pod ‘SVProgressHUD’, ‘~&gt; 2.0.3’<br>pod ‘MJRefresh’, ‘~&gt; 3.1.0’<br>pod ‘SDWebImage’, ‘~&gt; 3.7.6’</p><p>end</p><p><code>`</code><br>即添加</p><p>target ‘当前工程名’ do  </p><p>并在结尾加上  </p><p>end</p><p>####参考</p><p><a href="https://tomisacat.xyz/tech/2017/09/26/macos-high-sierra-with-cocoapods.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">升级 macOS High Sierra 后与 Cocoapods 的兼容问题</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
    </entry>
    
